
  Flygon    Ground Type Pokémon

  FLYGON is nicknamed “the elemental 
   spirit of the desert. ” Because 
  its flapping wings whip up a 
  cloud of sand, Flygon is 
  always enveloped in a sandstorm 
  while flying. 
